---
title: Double Seared Mexican Pork Loin Tacos with Creamy Slaw, Smashed Avo & Coriander
description: A juicy, flavourful pork steak is one of our favourite taco fillings, especially paired with a variety of bright accompaniments. A creamy radish slaw and mellow smashed avo fulfill those requirements perfectly is this crowd-pleasing dish. Throw it all in a
warm tortilla and you’re good to go!
